00:00:11,669 --> 00:00:21,664
♪In ancient times, a meteor fell♪

2
00:00:22,528 --> 00:00:29,920
♪Scorching Nanba Weald into land bare♪

3
00:00:30,336 --> 00:00:39,993
♪From Turquoise Land beneath the sun♪

4
00:00:41,088 --> 00:00:52,256
♪The evil Earth Fiends were born♪

5
00:00:55,168 --> 00:00:58,400
♪Marching in South Mountain's domain♪

6
00:00:58,400 --> 00:01:01,248
♪Sworn warriors raged for glory's gain♪

7
00:01:01,248 --> 00:01:03,328
♪Renamed guardians hold Yanguan true♪

8
00:01:03,328 --> 00:01:06,656
♪Peace in all lands, a priceless boon♪

9
00:01:12,224 --> 00:01:15,264
♪Seven hounds, two whips, one blade♪

10
00:01:15,264 --> 00:01:18,048
♪In rout and flight,
Earth Fiends escape♪

11
00:01:18,048 --> 00:01:20,839
♪Golden Gate seals fast♪

12
00:01:20,872 --> 00:01:25,243
♪South Mountain Hunters
on the righteous path♪

13
00:01:26,752 --> 00:01:37,024
♪South Mountain Hunters
on the righteous path♪

14
00:01:37,024 --> 00:01:41,216
=Love on the Turquoise Land=

15
00:01:41,216 --> 00:01:44,000
(This story is a work of fiction)

16
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:46,960
=Episode 5=

17
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:44,792
(Yan Tuo)

18
00:02:48,088 --> 00:02:51,828
(Yan Tuo, General Manager
of Roadsound Group)

19
00:02:54,072 --> 00:02:55,672
(Legal Representative, Lin Xirou)

20
00:02:58,584 --> 00:03:00,280
(Mr. Lu)

21
00:03:02,652 --> 00:03:04,611
Could you stop rushing me?

22
00:03:05,932 --> 00:03:07,092
The world has changed.

23
00:03:07,411 --> 00:03:09,372
Aesthetic tastes
are growing more unpredictable.

24
00:03:10,252 --> 00:03:11,411
What are you talking about?

25
00:03:12,252 --> 00:03:13,652
Your unmarketable new creation

26
00:03:13,691 --> 00:03:14,851
caught someone's eye.

27
00:03:15,332 --> 00:03:16,131
Really?

28
00:03:17,932 --> 00:03:18,812
I told him

29
00:03:19,131 --> 00:03:19,972
only drafts exist

30
00:03:19,972 --> 00:03:21,291
and the final product isn't done.

31
00:03:21,932 --> 00:03:22,652
Yet he insisted

32
00:03:22,972 --> 00:03:24,812
it's okay and he'd wait.

33
00:03:26,972 --> 00:03:28,212
Don't joke with me.

34
00:03:28,571 --> 00:03:29,652
Not sure if it's a joke.

35
00:03:30,052 --> 00:03:31,611
He prepaid for three pieces outright.

36
00:03:31,972 --> 00:03:32,772
He only wants

37
00:03:32,932 --> 00:03:33,972
to meet you

38
00:03:34,291 --> 00:03:35,372
and discuss art in person.

39
00:03:36,052 --> 00:03:36,972
Who is he?

40
00:03:37,332 --> 00:03:40,212
We can't pry about his background.

41
00:03:40,571 --> 00:03:42,212
Anyway, he's declared

42
00:03:42,652 --> 00:03:44,291
he'll buy whatever you produce.

43
00:03:44,972 --> 00:03:46,731
See? The world has changed.

44
00:04:12,652 --> 00:04:14,252
Are you sure nothing is wrong with him?

45
00:04:14,451 --> 00:04:15,851
A decent business owner.

46
00:04:16,372 --> 00:04:18,611
He started from scratch
through honest work.

47
00:04:18,812 --> 00:04:20,731
Since when do decent people
meet in cemeteries?

48
00:04:20,932 --> 00:04:22,492
It's why he's remarkable.

49
00:04:22,772 --> 00:04:23,451
Think about it.

50
00:04:23,652 --> 00:04:25,731
No invite to dinner
avoids dietary preferences.

51
00:04:25,932 --> 00:04:27,812
No invite to drinks
prevent seeming frivolous.

52
00:04:28,332 --> 00:04:30,972
No office meet avoids formal stiffness.

53
00:04:30,972 --> 00:04:31,812
No gallery meeting

54
00:04:31,851 --> 00:04:34,372
presumes you've outgrown such spaces.

55
00:04:34,492 --> 00:04:37,411
Which place has serene
yet meaningful setting

56
00:04:37,411 --> 00:04:38,812
suitable for discussing art freely

57
00:04:38,812 --> 00:04:40,372
and contemplating life deeply?

58
00:04:40,372 --> 00:04:41,851
Hotel executive lounge?

59
00:04:41,851 --> 00:04:42,731
Too pedestrian.

60
00:04:43,212 --> 00:04:44,372
Can a lounge allow you

61
00:04:44,372 --> 00:04:45,492
to explore life's essence,

62
00:04:45,891 --> 00:04:47,532
human destiny,

63
00:04:47,691 --> 00:04:49,812
or the end of life?

64
00:04:50,891 --> 00:04:51,812
I need to go.

65
00:04:52,171 --> 00:04:53,012
I see him.

66
00:04:59,772 --> 00:05:01,132
Is this how you treat clients?

67
00:05:02,572 --> 00:05:03,652
I'll require a refund.

68
00:05:03,931 --> 00:05:05,731
No need. I won't sell it to you.

69
00:05:05,931 --> 00:05:07,811
Your work is about rebirth, right?

70
00:05:10,572 --> 00:05:11,371
Madman.

71
00:05:16,692 --> 00:05:17,931
Though newly created

72
00:05:18,212 --> 00:05:19,291
with limited impact,

73
00:05:20,012 --> 00:05:21,251
I've read critiques

74
00:05:21,972 --> 00:05:23,291
that mostly interpret your work

75
00:05:23,611 --> 00:05:27,212
as depicting suffocation and confinement

76
00:05:28,051 --> 00:05:29,652
and conveying dark emotions.

77
00:05:31,692 --> 00:05:32,652
If you continue,

78
00:05:32,652 --> 00:05:34,332
you'll expose your ignorance.

79
00:05:38,491 --> 00:05:39,452
Whenever I come here,

80
00:05:40,132 --> 00:05:42,212
I don't feel death or fear.

81
00:05:43,491 --> 00:05:44,572
Your sculptures

82
00:05:44,652 --> 00:05:45,411
inexplicably

83
00:05:45,411 --> 00:05:46,611
don't oppress me.

84
00:05:47,291 --> 00:05:48,892
They evoke childbirth's struggle.

85
00:05:49,332 --> 00:05:51,692
Of course, it's agonizing

86
00:05:52,092 --> 00:05:53,371
for the mother and child,

87
00:05:54,171 --> 00:05:55,012
yet the miracle

88
00:05:55,012 --> 00:05:56,731
of new life emerging

89
00:05:57,132 --> 00:05:58,332
is the ultimate hope.

90
00:05:58,972 --> 00:05:59,491
So I believe

91
00:05:59,491 --> 00:06:00,772
you're fundamentally optimistic.

92
00:06:01,611 --> 00:06:03,452
True, I'm no art expert,

93
00:06:03,731 --> 00:06:04,772
but I'm not pretending.

94
00:06:04,892 --> 00:06:06,411
I genuinely admire your work.

95
00:06:10,772 --> 00:06:12,332
Let me share my interpretation.

96
00:06:12,332 --> 00:06:13,332
I'm all ears.

97
00:06:15,132 --> 00:06:16,332
Outsiders see

98
00:06:16,491 --> 00:06:17,811
a pampered heir

99
00:06:17,972 --> 00:06:19,371
living carefree.

100
00:06:19,772 --> 00:06:21,931
Even you've bought into this facade,

101
00:06:22,092 --> 00:06:22,731
trapped in

102
00:06:22,731 --> 00:06:24,892
an identity and fate you despise.

103
00:06:25,652 --> 00:06:27,452
If you truly appreciated my art,

104
00:06:28,092 --> 00:06:29,452
you'd recognize

105
00:06:29,491 --> 00:06:31,332
the dark emotions, such as suffocation

106
00:06:31,332 --> 00:06:32,452
and confinement

107
00:06:33,411 --> 00:06:34,851
that mirror your reality,

108
00:06:35,811 --> 00:06:36,972
instead of standing

109
00:06:37,132 --> 00:06:38,051
in front of me,

110
00:06:38,171 --> 00:06:39,772
spouting empty praise.

111
00:06:44,572 --> 00:06:46,051
Surprising depth of understanding

112
00:06:46,291 --> 00:06:47,851
for new acquaintances like us.

113
00:06:48,892 --> 00:06:51,452
I have no interest in understanding
a reckless madman

114
00:06:51,452 --> 00:06:52,931
who'd drown others with him in a car.

115
00:06:53,892 --> 00:06:55,452
My apologies. I acted rashly.

116
00:06:55,972 --> 00:06:57,772
I just wanted calm dialogue

117
00:06:57,772 --> 00:06:59,012
and honest communication.

118
00:06:59,411 --> 00:07:00,171
If you still think

119
00:07:00,171 --> 00:07:01,532
I'm mad after hearing me out,

120
00:07:02,491 --> 00:07:03,532
I'll put a stop to it.

121
00:07:03,532 --> 00:07:04,532
No more bothering.

122
00:07:12,772 --> 00:07:13,611
I'm not sure

123
00:07:13,611 --> 00:07:14,892
what you gain from being here.

124
00:07:15,772 --> 00:07:17,212
But this place makes me uneasy.

125
00:07:17,411 --> 00:07:18,132
Get to the point.

126
00:07:20,411 --> 00:07:23,332
I invited you here
to show you a piece of work.

127
00:07:25,212 --> 00:07:25,731
Work?

128
00:07:26,371 --> 00:07:27,012
A tombstone.

129
00:07:36,532 --> 00:07:37,411
A woman

130
00:07:38,611 --> 00:07:39,931
ruined my family.

131
00:07:41,012 --> 00:07:42,572
(Lin Xirou)
She even stole my mother's name.

132
00:07:43,572 --> 00:07:44,332
Lin Xirou is now

133
00:07:45,772 --> 00:07:47,652
in charge of the entire Roadsound Group,

134
00:07:47,652 --> 00:07:48,731
living carefree.

135
00:07:50,291 --> 00:07:53,012
This tombstone was erected for my mother

136
00:07:53,611 --> 00:07:54,972
and will also eventually be hers.

137
00:07:55,772 --> 00:07:58,291
Are you saying your biological mother
was named Lin Xirou,

138
00:07:59,092 --> 00:08:02,371
and the current Lin Xirou
of Roadsound Group

139
00:08:03,092 --> 00:08:04,491
is the one who killed her?

140
00:08:21,692 --> 00:08:22,892
I got you.

141
00:08:23,692 --> 00:08:24,411
Wait a bit longer.

142
00:08:24,532 --> 00:08:25,572
Dad will be home soon.

143
00:08:27,212 --> 00:08:27,811
Tuo.

144
00:08:28,371 --> 00:08:29,572
Dad.

145
00:08:30,291 --> 00:08:31,132
Sorry for being late.

146
00:08:31,371 --> 00:08:32,171
Here.

147
00:08:32,332 --> 00:08:34,371
Happy birthday.

148
00:08:34,371 --> 00:08:36,012
Such a beautiful toy car.

149
00:08:36,012 --> 00:08:36,972
Do you like it?

150
00:08:36,972 --> 00:08:38,851
Yes, I love it.

151
00:08:38,851 --> 00:08:41,051
Who is she?

152
00:08:42,692 --> 00:08:43,371
Honey,

153
00:08:44,532 --> 00:08:45,972
this is Li Ergou's sister,

154
00:08:46,132 --> 00:08:47,772
Shuangxiu. Li Shuangxiu.

155
00:08:49,332 --> 00:08:51,012
Since the baby you're carrying develops,

156
00:08:51,051 --> 00:08:52,772
and there's so much housework,

157
00:08:52,892 --> 00:08:54,731
Shuangxiu will stay here from now on.

158
00:08:54,851 --> 00:08:56,212
Order her around for chores

159
00:08:56,332 --> 00:08:57,892
like she's one of our family.

160
00:08:57,892 --> 00:08:59,532
Let me show you the place.

161
00:09:00,851 --> 00:09:03,171
You're about to give birth
and you're still doing chores.

162
00:09:03,171 --> 00:09:04,772
Dashan went to pick Tuo up from school.

163
00:09:04,931 --> 00:09:06,171
I'll go meet them halfway.

164
00:09:45,011 --> 00:09:45,731
Tuo,

165
00:09:47,812 --> 00:09:49,972
I have something very important to do.

166
00:09:51,011 --> 00:09:52,771
Be good and wait here, okay?

167
00:10:13,731 --> 00:10:17,131
Tuo, you may call me
Ms. Lin from now on.

168
00:10:17,812 --> 00:10:18,812
Ms. Lin.

169
00:10:24,491 --> 00:10:25,812
My full name is Lin Xirou.

170
00:10:40,851 --> 00:10:41,771
After that,

171
00:10:42,212 --> 00:10:43,251
she became

172
00:10:43,251 --> 00:10:44,692
the lady of our household.

173
00:10:47,812 --> 00:10:49,371
As a kid, I was clueless.

174
00:10:49,692 --> 00:10:50,771
For years,

175
00:10:50,771 --> 00:10:52,491
I had genuinely considered
her my family.

176
00:10:56,011 --> 00:10:57,371
After I eventually found

177
00:10:57,371 --> 00:10:58,651
my mother's diary,

178
00:10:58,771 --> 00:10:59,611
I realized...

179
00:11:04,212 --> 00:11:05,412
Why are you telling me this?

180
00:11:07,052 --> 00:11:07,972
Gou Ya

181
00:11:08,572 --> 00:11:10,452
was sent to the welfare home
by Lin Xirou.

182
00:11:11,692 --> 00:11:13,092
If he's truly an Earth Fiend,

183
00:11:14,251 --> 00:11:15,972
then Lin Xirou must control the key

184
00:11:16,052 --> 00:11:17,891
to transforming Earth Fiends
into human form.

185
00:11:19,292 --> 00:11:20,452
What else do you know?

186
00:11:20,812 --> 00:11:23,172
I've looked for a long time.
But she's too cautious.

187
00:11:24,292 --> 00:11:25,491
She has guarded against me.

188
00:11:26,292 --> 00:11:27,172
I found nothing.

189
00:11:27,812 --> 00:11:29,412
But now that Gou Ya is in trouble

190
00:11:29,932 --> 00:11:30,851
and I've met you

191
00:11:31,011 --> 00:11:32,172
and your organization,

192
00:11:32,771 --> 00:11:33,851
it gives me hope.

193
00:11:34,851 --> 00:11:35,972
I just want to know

194
00:11:35,972 --> 00:11:37,092
what I should do

195
00:11:37,371 --> 00:11:39,092
(Lin Xirou)
to avenge my mother.

196
00:11:40,651 --> 00:11:42,011
First, you need to find out

197
00:11:42,212 --> 00:11:43,572
exactly what Lin Xirou is.

198
00:11:43,891 --> 00:11:45,131
I don't care what she is.

199
00:11:46,891 --> 00:11:48,292
But I'm certain

200
00:11:48,531 --> 00:11:50,292
her connection
to Earth Fiends is unusual.

201
00:11:51,651 --> 00:11:52,851
If you truly oppose

202
00:11:52,851 --> 00:11:53,731
the Earth Fiends,

203
00:11:54,011 --> 00:11:54,771
working with me

204
00:11:55,371 --> 00:11:56,731
is a golden opportunity.

205
00:11:58,052 --> 00:12:00,731
You said it you considered
her your family.

206
00:12:00,891 --> 00:12:02,052
And she raised you.

207
00:12:03,011 --> 00:12:04,611
Do you think I'll take such a risk

208
00:12:04,731 --> 00:12:05,692
by working with you?

209
00:12:06,172 --> 00:12:08,292
If a hunter teams up with a wolf cub,

210
00:12:08,332 --> 00:12:09,972
they could destroy the entire wolf den.

211
00:12:09,972 --> 00:12:11,131
Isn't that worth the gamble?

212
00:12:11,332 --> 00:12:12,771
Don't flatter yourself as a wolf.

213
00:12:13,212 --> 00:12:15,332
You could be the snake
in the farmer's story.

214
00:12:18,371 --> 00:12:18,851
Fine.

215
00:12:20,692 --> 00:12:23,131
I know you're not afraid
of snakes or wolves.

216
00:12:25,011 --> 00:12:26,572
But you're afraid of water.

217
00:12:28,092 --> 00:12:30,251
I also know your home address
and workplace.

218
00:12:30,412 --> 00:12:31,932
Even your artistic philosophy.

219
00:12:32,692 --> 00:12:33,972
Driving a car into water

220
00:12:34,611 --> 00:12:35,572
was me going too far.

221
00:12:36,092 --> 00:12:37,412
But I can't promise

222
00:12:37,412 --> 00:12:38,812
I won't do it again.

223
00:12:45,212 --> 00:12:47,011
You're truly something.

224
00:12:47,771 --> 00:12:49,651
How rare to hear you say something kind.

225
00:12:50,491 --> 00:12:51,412
What do you mean?

226
00:12:53,052 --> 00:12:54,891
After hearing your life story earlier,

227
00:12:55,212 --> 00:12:56,172
I genuinely felt

228
00:12:56,172 --> 00:12:57,851
a slight sense of empathy.

229
00:12:58,251 --> 00:12:59,172
I even forgot about

230
00:12:59,172 --> 00:13:00,251
our past unpleasantness.

231
00:13:01,011 --> 00:13:01,932
But just now

232
00:13:02,011 --> 00:13:03,212
your words

233
00:13:03,491 --> 00:13:05,531
revived my disgust toward you.

234
00:13:06,251 --> 00:13:07,412
You have a way with people.

235
00:13:08,771 --> 00:13:09,891
If that's the case,

236
00:13:10,092 --> 00:13:11,651
your being immune to all persuasion

237
00:13:11,651 --> 00:13:12,812
and your sarcastic skills

238
00:13:12,812 --> 00:13:13,972
are thoroughly impressive.

239
00:13:14,812 --> 00:13:16,092
A truly dedicated

240
00:13:16,092 --> 00:13:17,572
and virtuous artist.

241
00:13:21,972 --> 00:13:22,572
Come with me.

242
00:13:23,172 --> 00:13:23,851
To where?

243
00:13:24,851 --> 00:13:26,491
I'll show you a sculpture.

244
00:13:50,078 --> 00:13:54,332
(Temple of the Righteous Lord)

245
00:13:54,332 --> 00:13:55,452
In ancient times,

246
00:13:56,052 --> 00:13:59,131
a meteor fell
into South Mountain's ancient woods.

247
00:14:00,052 --> 00:14:01,371
The meteor melted into the earth,

248
00:14:01,611 --> 00:14:02,771
turning the soil turquoise.

249
00:14:03,692 --> 00:14:07,212
Plants and animals mutated,
and strange occurrences multiplied.

250
00:14:08,092 --> 00:14:11,611
Then a type of light-fearing,

251
00:14:12,572 --> 00:14:13,651
carnivorous savage beasts

252
00:14:13,651 --> 00:14:15,172
started roaming South Mountain.

253
00:14:16,371 --> 00:14:17,812
The locals

254
00:14:17,932 --> 00:14:19,812
named those beasts Earth Fiends.

255
00:14:20,371 --> 00:14:22,731
Earth Fiends were brutal killers.

256
00:14:22,812 --> 00:14:24,131
People suffered terribly.

257
00:14:25,332 --> 00:14:25,972
Later,

258
00:14:26,692 --> 00:14:28,172
the emperor sent troops

259
00:14:28,692 --> 00:14:30,491
to drive the Earth Fiends underground.

260
00:14:31,572 --> 00:14:33,172
The soldiers who stayed

261
00:14:33,812 --> 00:14:35,611
abandoned their identities

262
00:14:35,891 --> 00:14:37,692
and called themselves
South Mountain Hunters.

263
00:14:37,692 --> 00:14:39,292
and swore enmity with Earth Fiends.

264
00:14:39,452 --> 00:14:40,731
This legacy continues today.

265
00:14:43,812 --> 00:14:45,011
Such detailed settings?

266
00:14:45,212 --> 00:14:46,572
Not writing a novel wastes them.

267
00:14:46,692 --> 00:14:47,851
I've said my piece.

268
00:14:48,651 --> 00:14:49,731
Believe what you will.

269
00:14:51,611 --> 00:14:52,212
Go on.

270
00:14:53,251 --> 00:14:54,572
Those injured by Earth Fiends

271
00:14:54,932 --> 00:14:56,092
develop filmy tissue

272
00:14:56,371 --> 00:14:58,371
over wounds after some time,

273
00:14:58,812 --> 00:15:00,011
like rooting and sprouting.

274
00:15:00,771 --> 00:15:02,412
Though revealing this to an outsider

275
00:15:02,771 --> 00:15:03,651
breaks our rules,

276
00:15:04,172 --> 00:15:05,531
soon I'll also be an outsider.

277
00:15:05,531 --> 00:15:06,332
It doesn't matter.

278
00:15:07,572 --> 00:15:08,371
Besides,

279
00:15:09,131 --> 00:15:10,172
what I described earlier

280
00:15:10,172 --> 00:15:11,611
were beast-like Earth Fiends.

281
00:15:12,491 --> 00:15:14,651
Humanoid ones might differ entirely.

282
00:15:15,172 --> 00:15:16,011
So

283
00:15:16,692 --> 00:15:18,651
you're also a South Mountain Hunter,

284
