and I'll grant you one in return.

570
00:36:59,732 --> 00:37:00,651
I pay each time.

571
00:37:00,972 --> 00:37:01,972
Why so calculative?

572
00:37:02,091 --> 00:37:03,011
Because I don't want

573
00:37:03,011 --> 00:37:04,211
to get entangled with you.

574
00:37:04,691 --> 00:37:06,131
Fine, as you say.

575
00:37:06,372 --> 00:37:07,332
Have you decided?

576
00:37:08,571 --> 00:37:09,932
What's your request this time?

577
00:37:12,611 --> 00:37:13,372
I've decided.

578
00:37:13,772 --> 00:37:15,571
Add me on WeChat. Scan my code.

579
00:37:21,571 --> 00:37:23,051
What brings you here today?

580
00:37:24,171 --> 00:37:26,772
I tried a braised dish spot
last night and found it good.

581
00:37:27,091 --> 00:37:28,452
The owner said they do breakfast,

582
00:37:28,452 --> 00:37:30,651
so I woke early to get you some.

583
00:37:31,252 --> 00:37:31,972
Try it first.

584
00:37:32,171 --> 00:37:33,091
I haven't tried it.

585
00:37:33,372 --> 00:37:35,091
Don't expect too much.
It might disappoint.

586
00:37:38,292 --> 00:37:39,131
Not bad.

587
00:37:39,372 --> 00:37:40,131
It's good?

588
00:37:40,491 --> 00:37:41,452
I'll buy more next time.

589
00:37:46,531 --> 00:37:49,051
I saw the report.
Our business are thriving.

590
00:37:49,611 --> 00:37:50,892
Don't just see the surface.

591
00:37:51,051 --> 00:37:52,252
Such a large group

592
00:37:52,412 --> 00:37:55,292
has countless trivial matters
beneath your notice.

593
00:37:55,732 --> 00:37:57,011
Don't focus only on now either.

594
00:37:57,292 --> 00:37:59,211
The future remains uncertain.

595
00:38:00,051 --> 00:38:01,491
If Roadsound's competitors

596
00:38:01,611 --> 00:38:03,651
had half your crisis awareness,

597
00:38:03,772 --> 00:38:05,611
they wouldn't have stayed
underfoot forever.

598
00:38:07,091 --> 00:38:09,651
You think these internal
and external troubles are imaginary?

599
00:38:11,892 --> 00:38:13,091
That's why I brought breakfast

600
00:38:13,292 --> 00:38:14,332
to ease your mind.

601
00:38:17,412 --> 00:38:18,491
I heard the other day

602
00:38:19,171 --> 00:38:20,252
Xiong caught someone.

603
00:38:20,252 --> 00:38:21,011
What happened?

604
00:38:27,531 --> 00:38:29,892
I know you want to help me,

605
00:38:30,211 --> 00:38:31,892
but some grassroots matters

606
00:38:32,171 --> 00:38:33,772
are better left untouched.

607
00:38:33,852 --> 00:38:34,611
Understood.

608
00:38:38,491 --> 00:38:39,812
The schedule is tight today.

609
00:38:40,211 --> 00:38:42,452
I need to visit the farm
before heading to the office.

610
00:38:43,651 --> 00:38:45,332
You even personally
oversee the planting?

611
00:38:45,611 --> 00:38:47,452
I need to check. I can't rest easy.

612
00:39:16,091 --> 00:39:17,732
Anyone here?

613
00:39:38,611 --> 00:39:41,972
Speak up now if you want less suffering.

614
00:39:45,531 --> 00:39:46,812
I'm old.

615
00:39:47,412 --> 00:39:48,452
I can't handle turmoil.

616
00:39:48,772 --> 00:39:49,772
Let's talk civilly.

617
00:39:53,051 --> 00:39:54,852
Where's the base
of South Mountain Hunters?

618
00:39:55,131 --> 00:39:56,171
How many members in total?

619
00:39:56,892 --> 00:39:58,972
What's your next action plan?

620
00:40:00,292 --> 00:40:01,011
The base...

621
00:40:02,292 --> 00:40:04,292
The base is at the South Heavenly Gate.

622
00:40:05,211 --> 00:40:08,691
Their numbers are hundreds of thousands,
and they are from a celestial army.

623
00:40:09,372 --> 00:40:13,292
And they plan to descend
to eradicate demons and monsters.

624
00:40:18,211 --> 00:40:19,372
Bad with essay questions?

625
00:40:19,852 --> 00:40:21,332
Then we'll make it multiple choice.

626
00:40:22,651 --> 00:40:23,732
How do you want to die?

627
00:40:24,412 --> 00:40:26,332
Bleed out? Heart extraction?

628
00:40:26,651 --> 00:40:28,011
Or live burial?

629
00:40:28,372 --> 00:40:30,812
If you'd brought Mrs. Hua with you,

630
00:40:31,412 --> 00:40:33,051
I'd choose live burial.

631
00:40:34,211 --> 00:40:36,131
We couldn't be together in life.

632
00:40:36,531 --> 00:40:37,932
Sharing a grave in death

633
00:40:38,051 --> 00:40:40,091
would fulfill my wish.

634
00:40:40,332 --> 00:40:41,972
That woman in the hospital

635
00:40:42,651 --> 00:40:43,611
is in such bad shape.

636
00:40:44,772 --> 00:40:46,892
She'll never speak again.

637
00:41:00,211 --> 00:41:01,531
He's quite spirited.

638
00:41:03,171 --> 00:41:04,252
Calm him down.

639
00:41:15,852 --> 00:41:16,812
Long time no see.

640
00:41:16,892 --> 00:41:18,211
Who are you?

641
00:41:19,372 --> 00:41:20,491
Twenty years ago,

642
00:41:20,932 --> 00:41:21,772
I offended you.

643
00:41:22,932 --> 00:41:23,732
Who?

644
00:41:26,611 --> 00:41:28,372
Don't tell me you're holding a grudge,

645
00:41:29,732 --> 00:41:31,732
wanting me to repay you with a leg?

646
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:51,343
(Greenhouse)

647
00:42:02,372 --> 00:42:04,292
Don't be fooled
by his usual carefree demeanor.

648
00:42:04,812 --> 00:42:06,772
He definitely has his own thoughts.

649
00:42:07,171 --> 00:42:08,491
He just buries them well.

650
00:42:09,491 --> 00:42:11,051
It's fine if it's not a deal-breaker.

651
00:42:11,651 --> 00:42:13,011
It's been many years.

652
00:42:13,772 --> 00:42:15,531
This whole mother-and-son-bond act

653
00:42:16,011 --> 00:42:18,091
has to continue, doesn't it?

654
00:42:18,412 --> 00:42:19,531
No matter what,

655
00:42:19,972 --> 00:42:21,892
Yan Tuo is my own son.

656
00:42:23,412 --> 00:42:25,892
Wake the old man below
and resume interrogation.

657
00:42:26,452 --> 00:42:28,452
We must extract information
about the Mad Blade.

658
00:42:28,611 --> 00:42:29,772
Understood. We'll handle it.

659
00:42:50,812 --> 00:42:51,651
(Lin Ling?)

660
00:42:54,011 --> 00:42:54,732
(Lin Ling?)

661
00:42:56,732 --> 00:42:58,171
(Where are you? Come out.)

662
00:42:59,531 --> 00:43:00,332
(Lin Ling.)

663
00:43:02,091 --> 00:43:02,892
(Lin Ling?)

664
00:43:04,972 --> 00:43:06,171
(Come out now.)

665
00:43:06,892 --> 00:43:07,852
(This is not fun.)

666
00:43:07,932 --> 00:43:09,611
(Ms. Lin will scold us
if she finds out.)

667
00:43:12,252 --> 00:43:13,011
(Lin Ling?)

668
00:43:13,691 --> 00:43:14,452
(Lin Ling?)

669
00:43:17,292 --> 00:43:17,972
(Lin Ling?)

670
00:43:45,976 --> 00:43:48,664
(Toxic and Hazardous)

671
00:44:16,312 --> 00:44:17,200
Lin Xirou.

672
00:44:20,560 --> 00:44:22,880
This humanoid Earth Fiend
and the Roadsound Group

673
00:44:22,920 --> 00:44:24,280
must be closely connected.

674
00:44:24,600 --> 00:44:26,080
This intel is crucial.

675
00:44:26,160 --> 00:44:27,600
We'll investigate immediately.

676
00:44:28,160 --> 00:44:28,800
Thank you.

677
00:44:29,600 --> 00:44:30,640
How's Sun Zhou?

678
00:44:32,440 --> 00:44:33,880
Overcast skies may make us

679
00:44:34,760 --> 00:44:35,720
miss the window.

680
00:44:36,200 --> 00:44:37,120
Do what you can.

681
00:44:37,320 --> 00:44:39,560
If even heaven won't save him,

682
00:44:39,920 --> 00:44:40,880
we can't help with that.

683
00:44:41,400 --> 00:44:42,200
Then

684
00:44:42,520 --> 00:44:44,840
we'll have to banish him to Golden Gate

685
00:44:45,000 --> 00:44:46,160
by Hunters' rules.

686
00:44:47,240 --> 00:44:48,680
Those wounded by Earth Fiends before

687
00:44:48,760 --> 00:44:50,800
and became infected
without timely fire purification

688
00:44:50,880 --> 00:44:52,120
were all Hunters

689
00:44:52,560 --> 00:44:54,040
who vowed to accept this fate.

690
00:44:54,040 --> 00:44:55,240
They were all prepared.

691
00:44:55,560 --> 00:44:57,080
But Sun Zhou is a civilian.

692
00:44:59,640 --> 00:45:00,840
For him,

693
00:45:01,720 --> 00:45:02,800
it's too cruel.

694
00:45:02,808 --> 00:45:03,465
Of course.

695
00:45:04,240 --> 00:45:05,880
I'll explore alternatives.

696
00:45:08,280 --> 00:45:12,600
♪If we don't retreat,
we'll go through it together♪

697
00:45:15,880 --> 00:45:16,800
Are you still there?

698
00:45:17,528 --> 00:45:17,968
Yes.

699
00:45:18,720 --> 00:45:19,680
Speaking of which,

700
00:45:20,400 --> 00:45:22,800
about the informant you mentioned,
who tipped you off

701
00:45:22,960 --> 00:45:24,840
about Lin Xirou and the Roadsound Group,

702
00:45:25,048 --> 00:45:26,090
who is he?

703
00:45:26,600 --> 00:45:27,720
You think he's unreliable?

704
00:45:27,840 --> 00:45:29,520
I'm worried for your safety.

705
00:45:29,720 --> 00:45:31,120
How did you connect with him?

706
00:45:33,240 --> 00:45:34,720
Maybe my unique constitution

707
00:45:34,920 --> 00:45:37,000
attracts oddities.

708
00:45:38,640 --> 00:45:40,520
We've got plenty of oddities here too.

709
00:45:41,360 --> 00:45:44,320
They're all here at the hospital
keeping watch over Mrs. Hua.

710
00:45:44,880 --> 00:45:47,160
I gotta go. It's starting up again.

711
00:45:47,768 --> 00:45:48,284
Okay.

712
00:45:52,904 --> 00:45:57,264
♪The shapeless fire
clings to matter to illuminate♪

713
00:45:57,264 --> 00:46:01,584
♪Yet malice in darkness
defies the flame's pursuit♪

714
00:46:01,584 --> 00:46:06,024
♪A noble name must do righteous deeds♪

715
00:46:06,024 --> 00:46:08,464
♪After sunrise,
even wise words falter in truth♪

716
00:46:08,464 --> 00:46:12,544
♪Heaven-forged fire
scorches flesh and bone♪

717
00:46:12,544 --> 00:46:16,904
♪Dig out the truth buried
beneath the earth♪

718
00:46:16,904 --> 00:46:21,264
♪Heaven-sent tides can't
quench this reckless fire♪

719
00:46:21,264 --> 00:46:25,624
♪If we don't retreat,
we'll go through it together♪

720
00:46:25,624 --> 00:46:29,984
♪Heaven-kindled flames are different♪

721
00:46:29,984 --> 00:46:34,264
♪Truth's madness is hiding
under the surface♪

722
00:46:34,264 --> 00:46:38,824
♪The large waves are rolling
towards the sky♪

723
00:46:38,824 --> 00:46:46,544
♪Farewell to the old times,
and scenes fade away one by one♪

